{"tid":729977,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"公屋9月起加租10%","createTime":"2018-07-05T04:30:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-05T07:02:15.000Z","uid":90802,"like":8,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"d2c3552f0f46af90262c36a3bb9852207896c1c9","tid":729977,"uid":90802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T04:30:58.000Z","msg":"公屋租金每兩年檢討一次，並按租戶家庭收入變動調整。2017年度公屋租戶的平均家庭收入較2015年度上升11.59%，因此，公屋租金將按機制加租10%，今年9月生效，每戶加租由34元至469元不等。<br />\n<br />\n房委會數字顯示，2017年12月的租金介乎346元至4690元，加租10%後，上調金額為34元至469元，平均上調金額約188元。<br />\n<br />\n截止2017年12月，香港共有約75.66萬戶公屋租戶，當中約11.99萬戶是綜援戶。另外，約59.48萬戶繳交正常租金，約1.71萬戶在租金援助計劃下接受資助並繳交正常租金，以及約2.48萬「富戶」繳交額外租金。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180705/s00001/1530764661268\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180705%2Fs00001%2F1530764661268&d=Vkdv0jVFtJcBGtldFPmmH8P%2FddU7lKBqZb2OVh9Tir8%3D&h=ef129ac8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180705%2Fs00001%2F1530764661268&h=9ca1ec3a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180705/s00001/1530764661268</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n依然係人生贏家<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26cfe16730f140ba19a13f7c4a1f2d2aeaacc4c4","tid":729977,"uid":2054,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T04:32:55.000Z","msg":"租樓跟隨加夠30%<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c9337e516d3b26a26750fa5106dd15d1e93c90f","tid":729977,"uid":106065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T04:46:57.000Z","msg":"加得幾舊水，跌都跌左啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bf2115ad554b7e76212d4d59888495c12ce6dd9","tid":729977,"uid":8867,"like":0,"di